             was indicted for <rs id="t17830226-38-off209" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830226-38-off209" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830226-38-off209" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17830226-38-cd210" type="crimeDate">3d of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830226-38-off209 t17830226-38-cd210"></join> instant, one gold watch chain, value 4 l. three stone seals, set in gold, value 3 l. one gold watch key, value 10 s. one gold trinket, value 10 s. one gold mourning ring, value 20 s. and one small silver key, value 2 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17830226-38-victim437" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     Western
                  <interp inst="t17830226-38-victim437" type="surname" value="Western"></interp>
