                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830226-38-off209 t17830226-38-victim437"></join>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17830226-38-viclabel211" type="occupation">Esq</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830226-38-victim437 t17830226-38-viclabel211"></join>.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner being a German, was asked by the Court, whether he chose to have one half of the Jury composed of his own countrymen, to which he replied in the affirmative, and the following Jury were sworn.)</p>
